quran[182]{c,v,t}:
  37,1,Mi woondirii saffiniraa…ói …óin saffaaji
  37,2,Mi woondirii soggiray…ói (duule) …óin soggugol
  37,3,"Mi woondirii janngiray…ói …óin, anndintinorgol"
  37,4,"Pellet, rewetee…óo mon On, ko bajjo"
  37,5,"Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde …óin …ói…ói, Jey…óo kadi fu…óir…óe …óen"
  37,6,"Men cu…óirii kammu (hikkii ngu) aduna ngun: cu…óaari koode …óen"
  37,7,e reenirgol (ngu) kala seytaane ra…óaandu
  37,8,"∆äi ha…ótanaaka he…óitagol mbatu [Malaa'ika'en] toowu ngu ngun; tawde hi…ói feroree e kala ba≈ã≈ãe"
  37,9,"ka ra…óagol (…ói). Hino woodani …ói kadi, lepte duumii…óe"
  37,10,"Si wanaa ndun bifti ndu e majji, jilannde [haala], ndu rewniree hoodere tufaynde"
  37,11,"Lamndo …ìe: si ko kam…ìe …ìuri sa…ótude tagude kaa ko …ìen …ìe Men tagi? Men tagirii …ìe kam…ìe, loopal narnungal"
  37,12,"Si ko woni, a haawi, hi…ìe jalnora"
  37,13,"Si …ìe waajaama, …ìe waajitortaa"
  37,14,"si …ìe yi'ii maande, …ìe jalkita"
  37,15,"…ìe wi'a: \"∆äum wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ìanngu ngu"
  37,16,"Eyoo si men maayii, men wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, haray ko men immintinoytee…ìe"
  37,17,Baabiraa…ìe amen adinoo…ìe …ìen kadi e minen
  37,18,"Maaku: \"Pellet! Hara le ko on hoynaa…ìe"
  37,19,"Anndon …óum, ko wuttaandu wooturu pet, tawee jaka yoo, hi…ìe ndaara"
  37,20,"∆Åe wi'a: Ee bone amen ! Ko ndee woni √ëalaande njo…ìdi kuu…óe"
  37,21,"Ko ndee woni √ëalaande √±aawoore, ko fennayno…óon fii mun"
  37,22,"Moo…ìee too√±u…ìe …ìen, e nandadii…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, e kon ko …ìe wonunoo e rewde"
  37,23,ko wonaa Alla. Soggiree…ìe ka laawol Jahiimi
  37,24,"Darnon …ìe, tawde ko …ìe lamnditetee…ìe"
  37,25,"Ko he…ìi on, on wallindirtaa"
  37,26,"Ko woni kam…ìe on hannde, ko …ìe jebbilii …ìe"
  37,27,"wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe fewtita …ìeya, …ìe lamndondira"
  37,28,"…ìe wi'a: \"Ko onon woni ko ardiranaynoo men, ka …ìa≈ã≈ãe √±aamo"
  37,29,"(Koohoo…ìe) …ìen wi'a: \"Ko woni kon, on mee…óaano wonnde gom…óim…ìe"
  37,30,"Doole woo men alanaano on. Si ko woni, on wonuno yim…ìe bew…ìe"
  37,31,"Konngol Joomi men ngol, jojjii e men; pellet, ko en mee…óoo…ìe [lepte …óen]"
  37,32,"Men bewinno on, tawde hay menen, ko men bewnoo…ìe"
  37,33,"Kam…ìe on nden √±alnde, ko …ìe hawtoytee…ìe ka lepte"
  37,34,Ko nii Menen Men huuwirta bom…ìe …ìen
  37,35,"Kam…ìe si …ìe wi'anooma: \"Rewetee…óo alaa si wanaa Alla\", …ìe mawnintinoo"
  37,36,"…ìe wi'a: \"Kere men accitiray rewetee…ói amen …óin, fii yimoowo haangaa…óo"
  37,37,"Si ko woni, (Nulaa…óo) on ko goonga ardi, o goongini Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,38,"Pellet, ko on mee…óay …ìe lepte muusu…óe …óen"
  37,39,"On yo…ìitetaake, si wanaa yeru kon ko huuwayno…óon"
  37,40,si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Alla la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,41,"hino woodani …ìen …óon, fanndaari anndaandi"
  37,42,"muuyantee…ói, kadi ko …ìe teddinaa…ìe"
  37,43,ka Aljannaaji neeminii…ói
  37,44,"e hoore dan…óe, ko …ìe fewtondir…ìe"
  37,45,"Hara kore hino wannginii e ma…ì…ìe, immorde e …ìulirde"
  37,46,"daneere, lew√±unde, fii yaroo…ìe"
  37,47,"muusu hoore alaa e majjam, wanaa …óam siwrinirtee…ìe …óam"
  37,48,"Hino woodani …ìe (ton): ra…ì…ìidu…ìe ndaar…óe, yaaja gitee…ìe"
  37,49,wa'u…ìe wa boofo maraa…óe
  37,50,"Wo…ó…ìe e ma…ì…ìe fewtita …ìeya, …ìe lamndondira"
  37,51,"Go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe wi'a: \"Min mi…óo marunoo wonndii…óo"
  37,52,"wi'aynoo…óo: \"Kere ko a jeyaa…óo e googim…ìe …ìen"
  37,53,"Eyoo si en maayii, en wontii mbullaari e ∆¥i'e, haray ko en yo…ìitoytee…ìe"
  37,54,"O wi'a: \"Taw si …óon yi…ói ∆¥eewude"
  37,55,"O ∆¥eewa, o haynoo oya ka tummbo Dulbunge"
  37,56,"o wi'a: \"Mi woondirii Alla ! A e…ì…ìuno fii no mi halkorde"
  37,57,"Si wanaano mo∆¥∆¥ere Joomi am nden, mi tawdeteno e [leptetee…ìe …ìen]"
  37,58,Wonaa non enen maayataa
  37,59,"si wanaa maayde men aranere nden, en wonaali kadi leptetee…ìe"
  37,60,"Pellet, ko …óum …óoo woni maloore mawnunde nden"
  37,61,"Ko fii sugu …óum …óoo, woni yo golloo…ìe gollan"
  37,62,"Hara ko …óum …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude jipporde, kaa ko leggal \"Zaqquumi\" [ngal haa…óungal]"
  37,63,Men wa…óii ngal jarrabuyee too√±u…ìe …ìen
  37,64,"Ngal, ko leggal yaltayngal ka tummbere Dulbunge"
  37,65,"Dim…óe maggal, hino wa'i wa ko'e seytanooji"
  37,66,"Kam…ìe on, pellet, ko e maggal …ìe nyaamirta, …ìe hebbinira ngal deedi ma…ì…ìe"
  37,67,"Refti hino woodani …ìe e dow maggal, njaram fatinaa…óam"
  37,68,"Refti ruttorde ma…ì…ìe nden, ko ka Dul…ìoowe"
  37,69,"∆Åe tawu baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, ko majjunoo…ìe"
  37,70,…ìe woni e yaccagol jokka ba…óteeji ma…ì…ìe
  37,71,"Gom…óii, ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e aram…ìe …ìen, majjiino, ado ma…ì…ìe"
  37,72,"Gom…óii le, Men nuluno e ma…ì…ìe, jertinoo…ìe"
  37,73,"Kono ndaaru ba…ótane …ìen jertinanoo…ìe, no wa'unoo"
  37,74,"Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Alla, la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,75,"Gom…óii Nuuhu nodduno Men, Men mo∆¥∆¥ii jaabotoo…ìe"
  37,76,"Men da…óni mo, kanko e yim…ìe makko …ìen, e suno mawnungo ngon"
  37,77,"Men wa…ói geyngol makko ngol, heddotoo…ìe …ìen"
  37,78,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ìe …ìen"
  37,79,"Kisal wonii e Nuuhu, e nder winndere nden"
  37,80,Ko non woni ko Men warjorta mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe …ìen
  37,81,"Kanko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  37,82,Refti Men yooli heddii …ìe …ìen
  37,83,"Hino jeyanoo e jokku…ìe mo …ìen, Ibraahiima"
  37,84,"Tuma nde ardunoo ka Joomi makko, e …ìernde hisunde"
  37,85,"Nde o maakannoo ben makko e yim…ìe mun …ìen: \"Ko hon…óum rewoton"
  37,86,"E ko rewetee…ói fefindaa…ói, ko wanaa Alla, faala…óon"
  37,87,Ko sikku…óon e Joomiraawo tageefo ngon
  37,88,O ndaariri ndaarande ka koode
  37,89,"o maaki: \"Ko mi nawnu…óo"
  37,90,"∆Åe acci mo, …ìe hucciti"
  37,91,"O moltii e rewetee…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, o maaki: \"E on √±aamataa"
  37,92,"Ko he…ìi on, on wowlataa"
  37,93,"O moltorani …ói, piyirgol …ói √±aamo ngon"
  37,94,"∆Åe fewri ka makko, hi…ìe yaawno"
  37,95,"O maaki: \"E on reway kon ko lesu…óon"
  37,96,"hara le ko Alla tagi on, e kon ko golloton"
  37,97,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Mahanee mo maadi, bugo…óon mo ka dul…ìayange"
  37,98,∆Åe faandanii mo feere; kono Men wa…ói …ìe sooyube …ìen
  37,99,"O maaki: \"Min on, ko mi feroowo ka Joomi am, aray nde O fewnata lam"
  37,100,"Joomi am, ye…óam ge…ìal mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe"
  37,101,"Men wewliniri mo, ge…óal mu√±√±ii…óo"
  37,102,"Nde on yottinoo e makko jahal, [Ibraahiima] maaki: \"Ko an …ìi…ó…óo am, min mi yi'ii e …óoyngol, wonnde mi…óo hirse. Ndaaru ko yi'u…óaa\". [Ismaa'iila] maaki: \"Ko onon yo baaba'en, wa…óee ko yamira…óon kon, on tawoyay lam, si Alla ja…ìii, jeyaa…óo e mu√±ii…ìe …ìen"
  37,103,"Nde …ìe jebbilaninoo (ymiroore Alla nden), o hippiri mo tiinde nden"
  37,104,"Men noddiri mo wiide: \"ko yo Ibraahiima"
  37,105,"Pellet, a goonginii koy…óol ngol. Ko Menen Men yo…ìirte mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen"
  37,106,"Pellet, ko …óum …óoo woni jarrabuyee …ìanngu…óo on"
  37,107,Men soktiri mo kirse maw…óe
  37,108,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ìe …ìen"
  37,109,Kisiyee wonii e Ibraahiima
  37,110,Ko wano nii Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥inoo…ìe …ìen
  37,111,"Kanko, ko o jeyaa…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  37,112,"Men wewlintiniri Ishaaqa, Annabaajo jeyaa…óo e mo∆¥∆¥u…ìe …ìen"
  37,113,"Men hebbini barki e makko e Ishaaqa. Hino e geyngol ma…ì…ìe ngol: mo∆¥∆¥in…óo, e too√±u…óo hoore-mun …ìanngini"
  37,114,Gom…óii Men mo∆¥∆¥ike e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna
  37,115,"Men da…óni …ìe, kam…ìe e yim…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, e ngo∆¥o mawnungo"
  37,116,"Men walli …ìe, …ìe woni foolu…ìe …ìen"
  37,117,Men okki …ìe Deftere …ìannginnde nden
  37,118,"Men fewniri …ìe, e laawol focciingol ngol"
  37,119,"Men accani …ìe mantoore, e sakkitii…ìe …ìen"
  37,120,Kisal wonii e dow Muusaa e Haaruuna
  37,121,Ko wano nii Men yo…ìitirta mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe …ìen
  37,122,"Kam…ìe …ói…óo, ko …ìe jeyanoo…ìe e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,124,"Janto nde o maakannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"E on hulataa [Alla]"
  37,125,"E ko \"Ba'ala\" rewoton, accon …ìur…óo mo∆¥∆¥ude tagu On"
  37,126,"Woni Alla, Jey…óo on, Jeyi baabiraa…ìe mon adinoo…ìe …ìen"
  37,127,"∆Åe fenni mo, awa non, ko …ìe tawnoytee…ìe (ka lepte)"
  37,128,Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Alla la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,129,"Men accani mo mantoore, e sakkitii…ìe …ìen"
  37,130,Kisal wonii e dow Ilyaasiina'en
  37,131,Ko wano nii Men yo…ìirta mo∆¥∆¥im…ìe …ìen
  37,132,"Kanko, ko o jeyanoo…óo e jeyaa…ìe Amen gom…óim…ìe …ìen"
  37,133,"Pellet, Luutu kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,134,"Janto nde Men da…óndunoo mo, kanko e …ìeynguure makko nden fow"
  37,135,"si wonaa nayeeja debba, tawaa…óo e luttunoo…ìe …ìen"
  37,136,refti Men o∆¥∆¥i heddii …ìe …ìen
  37,137,"Onon non, hi…óon rewa e hoore-ma…ì…ìe, dawol mon"
  37,138,e ka jemma. E on haqqiltaa
  37,139,"Pellet, Yuunusa kadi, ko jeyanoo…óo e Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,140,Janto nde o dogirnoo ka laana hebbinaaka
  37,141,"o urbinii, o jeyaa e foolaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,142,"Linngii ngii mo…ói mo, ko o felnii…óo"
  37,143,Si wanaano tawde himo jeyanoo e subbunhinotoo…ìe …ìen
  37,144,"o √±ii…ìayno e reedu maggii, haa √±alnde …ìe immintinoytee"
  37,145,"Men werlii mo ka ladde, ko o nawnu…óo"
  37,146,"Men fu…óini e mayre, leggal buudi"
  37,147,"Men nuli mo e ujune teemeder yim…ìe, maa ko …ìuri"
  37,148,"∆Åe gom…óini, Men dakmiti …ìe haa e dumunna"
  37,149,"Lamndii …ìe:\" E ko Joomi maa woodanta …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe, kam…ìe kan wor…ìe"
  37,150,"Kaa Men tagir Malaa'ika'en rew…óinaa…ói, hara ko …ìe seedii…ìe"
  37,151,"Faamee, kam…ìe e pepindaale ma…ì…ìe …óen, hi…ìe wi'a"
  37,152,"Allah jibinii\"; pellet, …ìe fanay"
  37,153,Hara O su…ìay …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe …ìen e dow wor…ìe …ìen
  37,154,"Ko he…ìi on, si …óon √±aawira non"
  37,155,E on miijitottaako
  37,156,Kaa hi…óon jogii hujja …ìanngu…óo
  37,157,"Haray addee deftere mon nden, si wonii ko on goongu…ìe"
  37,158,"∆Åe wa…ói hakkunde Makko e Malaa'ika'en, asko; hara non, Malaa'ka'en no anndi, …ìen ko tawnoytee…ìe (ka lepte)"
  37,159,"Senayee woodani Allah, e kon ko …ìe sifotoo"
  37,160,Si wanaa jeyaa…ìe Allah la…ì…ìinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,161,Anndon onon e ko rewoton kon
  37,162,"on wonaali majjinoo…ìe …óum [go…ó…óo goo]"
  37,163,si wanaa taw…óo on ko naatoowo ka Dul…ìaynge
  37,164,"[Malaa'ika'en wi'i]: \"Alaa e amen, mo alanaa …óum, darorde anndaande"
  37,165,Ko menen woni saffinaa…ìe …ìen
  37,166,Ko menen kadi woni subbunhinotoo…ìe …ìen
  37,167,∆Åe woniino e wi'ugol
  37,168,"Hara Deftere iwnde e adinoo…ìe …ìen, no woodannoo men"
  37,169,men wonayno jeyaa…ìe Allah la…ì…ìinaa…ìe
  37,170,"∆Åe yeddi nde, kono aray …ìe anndoya"
  37,171,"Gom…óii Konngol Amen ardinoke, fii jeyaa…ìe Amen, Nulaa…ìe …ìen"
  37,172,"wonnde pellet, ko kam…ìe woni walletee…ìe …ìen"
  37,173,"e wonnde ko konu Amen ngun, woni fooloo…ìe …ìen"
  37,174,"∆äuurno …ìee, haa e saanga"
  37,175,"ndaaraa …ìe, …ìe aray yi'ude"
  37,176,E hara ko lepte Amen …óen …ìe he√±orta
  37,177,"Si …óe jippike ka tannde (dingiral)ma…ì…ìe, haray bimmbi waajonoo…ìe …ìen bonii"
  37,178,"∆äuurno …ìee, haa e saanga"
  37,179,"ndaaraa, …ìe aray yi'ude"
  37,180,"Senayee woodanii Joomi maa, Jey…óo teddungal, e kon ko …ìe sifotoo"
  37,181,Kisyee wonii e Nulaa…ìe …ìen
  37,182,"Yettoore woodani Allah, Jey…óo winndere nden"